Gov. David Dewhurst's announced plan to fund a $60 million a year "permanent surge" on the border. 

David also talks with investigative journalist and the editor of Storyleak, Anthony Gucciardi, in-studio about Obama's dictatorial policies. 

Other topics up for discussion today include the sad state of the economy, the minimum wage and the hypocrisy of the globalist Trans-Pacific Partnership scheme.
